WEBVTT

01:35.780 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 2]

01:50.710 --> 01:51.570
Have you made up your mind?

01:52.560 --> 01:53.850
Once I catch Xiaowei,

01:55.150 --> 01:56.540
I'll be able to get into the Shilin Sect.

01:58.040 --> 01:58.770
Then,

02:00.950 --> 02:01.980
I'll kill the Dragon Deity.

02:08.350 --> 02:09.540
One

02:10.710 --> 02:11.620
of you here

02:13.030 --> 02:15.060
is the heart-ripping killer I'm after.

02:37.190 --> 02:37.890
It was him!

02:38.710 --> 02:39.450
It was him!

02:39.860 --> 02:41.880
Wu was the one who tied me up!

03:12.800 --> 03:13.540
He's been poisoned.

03:14.520 --> 03:15.260
How could that be?

03:17.240 --> 03:17.820
Shengwei,

03:18.240 --> 03:18.940
don't worry.

03:20.310 --> 03:21.010
A powerful demon hunter

03:21.010 --> 03:22.440
from the Shilin Sect is right here.

03:23.310 --> 03:24.130
He'll be fine.

03:26.560 --> 03:28.500
Someone must have poisoned him.

03:29.840 --> 03:31.890
My brother-in-law has never had enemies.

03:33.030 --> 03:33.940
Who would do this?

03:35.750 --> 03:37.730
It seems to be a slow-acting poison.

03:38.000 --> 03:39.540
It'd have to be administered little by little

03:39.590 --> 03:40.410
over time.

03:40.870 --> 03:42.410
Only someone close to him

03:42.410 --> 03:43.100
could've done it.

03:44.590 --> 03:46.010
If we'd found him any later,

03:46.360 --> 03:47.940
he would've been beyond saving.

03:50.590 --> 03:51.170
But even now,

03:51.840 --> 03:53.570
he's in bad shape.

03:54.980 --> 03:55.820
Normally,

03:56.030 --> 03:57.220
I could use magic

03:57.310 --> 03:58.690
to draw the poison out of his body.

03:59.560 --> 04:02.480
But my ring's sacred power

04:02.480 --> 04:03.420
is down to a tenth.

04:04.120 --> 04:05.010
I can't save him.

04:06.310 --> 04:07.290
Master Ji Ling,

04:07.520 --> 04:08.410
not even you can save him?

04:12.310 --> 04:12.980
Wei Qing,

04:14.470 --> 04:15.100
Wei Qing,

04:15.960 --> 04:16.570
Wei Qing...

04:18.430 --> 04:19.570
How did this happen?

04:28.720 --> 04:29.490
If we find the antidote

04:29.510 --> 04:30.510
soon enough,

04:30.510 --> 04:31.490
there may still be hope.

04:34.670 --> 04:35.400
I have...

04:36.020 --> 04:36.570
Let's go.

04:37.950 --> 04:39.020
- I... I really do have... - Come on, let's go.

05:01.670 --> 05:03.070
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

05:04.600 --> 05:05.250
No need.

05:06.000 --> 05:07.170
There's another injured person here.

05:09.720 --> 05:11.930
Miss Yu, your neck wound

05:12.040 --> 05:12.900
looks pretty deep.

05:14.000 --> 05:15.460
If it's not treated properly,

05:16.240 --> 05:17.170
it'll scar.

05:18.510 --> 05:19.410
But,

05:20.750 --> 05:22.220
Mr. Ji, you just said

05:22.750 --> 05:24.700
your sacred power is down to only a tenth.

05:25.270 --> 05:26.730
Can you still heal me?

05:28.430 --> 05:29.540
There's another way.

05:32.190 --> 05:33.730
A special wound powder from the Shilin Sect.

05:35.630 --> 05:36.340
It works even better.

05:43.920 --> 05:45.490
You... you don't want it?

05:48.870 --> 05:50.270
Mr. Ji, would you

05:50.270 --> 05:51.340
be so kind

05:51.870 --> 05:53.340
as to apply it for me?

05:54.620 --> 05:55.730
I'm not familiar with this.

05:57.430 --> 05:58.460
I'm afraid I'll do it wrong.

06:03.240 --> 06:03.810
Sure.

06:38.800 --> 06:39.490
Done.

06:42.310 --> 06:43.290
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

06:44.830 --> 06:45.460
You're welcome.

06:51.600 --> 06:52.430
Miss Yu Wei,

06:53.510 --> 06:55.410
- have we...? - Mr. Ji,

06:56.270 --> 06:58.340
we'd better head back to the front hall.

06:59.480 --> 07:01.370
They may be questioning Master Wu.

07:03.630 --> 07:04.250
All right.

07:08.560 --> 07:10.340
I was worried about Master Wei's safety,

07:10.920 --> 07:12.020
so I secretly asked

07:12.020 --> 07:13.980
Master Wu Shiguang to pose as the groom.

07:15.830 --> 07:16.780
Master Wu Shiguang,

07:17.870 --> 07:18.700
wait.

07:20.480 --> 07:21.900
Master Wei won't hire you,

07:22.870 --> 07:23.850
but I will.

07:27.190 --> 07:28.020
Steward Luo,

07:29.310 --> 07:30.660
my brother-in-law trusted you so much,

07:31.000 --> 07:31.810
yet you colluded

07:31.830 --> 07:33.550
with some demon hunter of questionable background

07:33.630 --> 07:35.060
to pull something this absurd.

07:35.680 --> 07:37.060
If you really wanted help,

07:37.390 --> 07:39.460
you should've hired a real demon hunter from the Shilin Sect.

07:40.310 --> 07:40.980
Am I right,

07:41.950 --> 07:42.730
Mr. Ji?

07:44.950 --> 07:45.700
Exactly.

07:47.920 --> 07:48.660
But

07:49.040 --> 07:51.140
Steward Luo's concern wasn't misplaced.

07:51.510 --> 07:52.700
Master Wei was poisoned.

07:53.000 --> 07:54.250
Someone really was trying to harm him.

07:55.830 --> 07:56.780
You're suspicious of a human

07:57.160 --> 07:58.220
instead of a demon?

07:59.360 --> 08:00.810
The fox demon is clearly in the Wei mansion.

08:01.510 --> 08:02.610
Two people died here last night.

08:03.390 --> 08:04.020
One of them

08:04.070 --> 08:05.780
was even a single-flower hunter from the Shilin Sect.

08:06.870 --> 08:07.810
The culprit was brutal.

08:08.040 --> 08:08.850
If I hadn't

08:08.870 --> 08:10.170
hidden Master Wei away in advance,

08:11.040 --> 08:11.810
then maybe...

08:15.560 --> 08:16.490
I can still drink.

08:17.390 --> 08:18.220
I can still drink.

08:19.040 --> 08:19.700
Where's the wine?

08:20.560 --> 08:21.220
Wine...

08:22.480 --> 08:23.260
Let's sit down.

08:23.560 --> 08:25.340
Prepare a bowl of hangover soup for Young Master Liu.

08:25.750 --> 08:26.340
Yes, madam.

08:29.680 --> 08:31.020
Why would a demon need poison to kill?

08:31.390 --> 08:32.410
It could just rip out hearts.

08:35.870 --> 08:37.180
The fake groom has spoken.

08:39.030 --> 08:39.850
Shouldn't the fake bride

08:40.240 --> 08:41.700
explain herself too?

08:43.600 --> 08:44.730
Stop calling me

08:44.730 --> 08:45.890
the fake bride.

08:46.790 --> 08:47.820
I have a name.

08:48.870 --> 08:49.770
My surname, Wu,

08:50.790 --> 08:52.130
means "mist."

08:53.510 --> 08:55.100
My given name, Wangyan, means "reckless speech."

08:56.550 --> 08:57.420
My parents gave me

08:57.440 --> 08:58.300
this name

08:58.630 --> 09:00.340
to remind me

09:00.840 --> 09:01.850
not to speak rashly.

09:02.670 --> 09:03.580
So,

09:04.360 --> 09:06.100
when I say I'm not a fox demon,

09:06.910 --> 09:07.770
I'm not.

09:10.390 --> 09:12.100
But you do carry

09:12.150 --> 09:13.180
a fox demon's aura.

09:13.600 --> 09:14.580
Master Ji Ling,

09:14.960 --> 09:16.100
have you been paying attention to me?

09:16.840 --> 09:18.250
If you're so interested in me,

09:18.840 --> 09:19.980
why don't we talk in private?

09:23.440 --> 09:24.250
That won't be necessary.

09:26.080 --> 09:26.880
A man and a woman

09:26.880 --> 09:28.250
shouldn't meet in private so casually.

09:28.960 --> 09:29.610
Whatever you have to say,

09:29.840 --> 09:31.220
say it here in front of everyone.

09:44.030 --> 09:44.890
I've been

09:45.480 --> 09:47.010
searching for this nine-tailed fox for years.

09:47.840 --> 09:48.730
It took a lot to get my hands

09:48.790 --> 09:49.730
on this severed tail.

09:50.390 --> 09:52.180
Its connection to the fox demon

09:52.790 --> 09:54.220
led me all the way here to the Wei mansion.

09:55.840 --> 09:57.420
It does carry the aura of a nine-tailed fox.

09:58.390 --> 09:59.940
Why are you looking for that fox demon?

10:00.600 --> 10:01.650
Do you have some grudge against her?

10:03.840 --> 10:04.730
You could say that.

10:06.390 --> 10:07.850
That nine-tailed fox

10:08.000 --> 10:09.130
is named Xiaowei.

10:10.080 --> 10:12.250
When she fell into hardship, a mortal saved her.

10:13.000 --> 10:13.770
To repay the debt,

10:14.320 --> 10:15.850
she kept killing people and ripping out hearts

10:16.840 --> 10:18.370
to preserve her human form and spiritual power,

10:18.720 --> 10:20.130
all so she could find her savior

10:20.440 --> 10:21.460
in the vast sea of people

10:21.840 --> 10:23.890
and keep him safe and happy for life.

10:24.750 --> 10:25.770
Unfortunately,

10:26.910 --> 10:28.010
her wish was never fulfilled.

10:30.840 --> 10:32.060
More than a millennium has passed,

10:33.200 --> 10:34.700
yet she's still obsessed

10:35.680 --> 10:36.980
with finding the one who saved her.

10:37.920 --> 10:39.330
Did Master Wei

10:40.440 --> 10:41.650
save her?

10:42.510 --> 10:43.420
I think so.

10:44.270 --> 10:45.220
If that's the case,

10:45.320 --> 10:47.010
she must want to kill her rival in love.

10:47.550 --> 10:49.820
That's why I posed as the bride

10:50.080 --> 10:51.060
and waited for her to walk into the trap.

10:52.080 --> 10:52.940
But instead,

10:53.630 --> 10:55.010
all I caught was a foolish pig.

11:01.320 --> 11:02.130
These days,

11:02.960 --> 11:04.650
demons all know how to wear painted human skin.

11:05.320 --> 11:05.980
They no longer need

11:06.000 --> 11:07.100
to devour human hearts

11:07.100 --> 11:08.010
to maintain their human form.

11:09.720 --> 11:10.490
Then why is Xiaowei

11:11.670 --> 11:12.650
killing people?

11:14.200 --> 11:15.610
Demons are evil by nature.

11:16.240 --> 11:18.250
Do they need a reason to kill?

11:20.440 --> 11:21.650
Demons are bad,

11:22.840 --> 11:23.730
but humans

11:24.940 --> 11:26.530
aren't much better.

11:29.390 --> 11:30.350
Humans aren't born

11:30.350 --> 11:31.610
knowing virtue and decency,

11:32.390 --> 11:33.180
and demons

11:34.000 --> 11:36.180
aren't always bent on evil either.

11:37.630 --> 11:38.700
But either way,

11:40.000 --> 11:40.700
there has to be

11:42.150 --> 11:43.340
a reason for a killing.

11:44.440 --> 11:45.250
Maybe

11:45.630 --> 11:47.650
she was badly weakened after losing a tail

11:48.750 --> 11:50.300
and needed to eat human hearts

11:51.510 --> 11:52.580
to maintain her human form.

11:54.720 --> 11:56.580
Since everyone here is under suspicion,

11:57.200 --> 11:58.490
until Xiaowei is caught,

11:59.550 --> 12:00.940
no one should leave the Wei mansion.

12:05.320 --> 12:06.100
That's unnecessary.

12:06.750 --> 12:07.460
Xiaowei's savior

12:07.480 --> 12:08.490
is now

12:08.490 --> 12:09.520
lying in bed dying.

12:09.750 --> 12:10.940
She'll definitely find a way to save him.

12:11.840 --> 12:12.730
Why would she leave?

12:13.150 --> 12:14.490
That's only your guess.

12:16.600 --> 12:17.580
Are you Xiaowei?

12:22.440 --> 12:23.650
The fabric house is busy.

12:24.200 --> 12:25.460
Everything inside and out needs my attention.

12:25.910 --> 12:27.250
I can't stay here forever.

12:28.000 --> 12:29.700
If you want to leave, you can.

12:31.240 --> 12:32.650
But you'll have to cooperate with me

12:33.360 --> 12:34.770
and accept my Blood Binding Seal.

12:35.320 --> 12:37.130
That way, even if you flee

12:38.000 --> 12:38.850
to the ends of the earth,

12:39.150 --> 12:40.340
I'll still be able to track you.

12:42.270 --> 12:42.940
Wait.

12:43.550 --> 12:45.490
We're demon hunters from the Shilin Sect.

12:46.080 --> 12:47.180
Do we have to do that too?

12:48.600 --> 12:49.610
Demons can wear human skin,

12:50.440 --> 12:51.250
and people can lie.

12:52.150 --> 12:52.980
How do I know

12:53.510 --> 12:54.250
if you're really

12:54.270 --> 12:55.220
from the Shilin Sect?

12:56.870 --> 12:57.980
You scared me.

12:59.550 --> 13:00.250
Fine.

13:00.510 --> 13:01.340
The innocent have nothing to fear.

13:02.360 --> 13:03.250
We'll cooperate.

13:42.870 --> 13:43.700
A death curse?

13:48.360 --> 13:49.530
What... what did you do?

13:52.750 --> 13:53.650
Master Wu,

13:54.270 --> 13:55.460
what did you do?

13:56.150 --> 13:57.340
Why do you want us dead?

13:59.630 --> 14:00.220
I didn't do this.

14:05.480 --> 14:06.220
Xiaowei did.

14:07.240 --> 14:08.490
Xiaowei?

14:12.510 --> 14:14.700
How powerful is that fox demon?

14:15.280 --> 14:17.480
She managed to brand all of us

14:18.590 --> 14:19.940
with a death curse mark

14:19.940 --> 14:20.730
without anyone noticing?

14:20.730 --> 14:21.220
No,

14:22.240 --> 14:23.490
that's not necessarily true.

14:24.360 --> 14:25.790
She might have set conditions

14:25.910 --> 14:27.250
so the curse would be triggered automatically.

14:28.030 --> 14:29.530
For example, she could make it so

14:29.600 --> 14:30.820
that if all of us did something

14:31.200 --> 14:32.490
or failed to do something at the same time,

14:32.960 --> 14:33.980
the death curse would be triggered.

14:37.870 --> 14:38.370
I get it now!

14:42.870 --> 14:44.130
None of us brought a wedding gift.

14:45.510 --> 14:46.180
Gentlemen,

14:46.750 --> 14:47.730
to prevent confusion,

14:48.120 --> 14:49.060
please tell us your names

14:49.390 --> 14:50.490
and leave your gifts here.

14:51.720 --> 14:53.370
You and Wu Wangyan were posing as the groom and bride,

14:53.750 --> 14:54.980
so naturally, you didn't prepare any gifts.

14:55.600 --> 14:56.370
Xiaowei

14:56.960 --> 14:58.770
must've linked the curse to the gift record.

15:02.460 --> 15:05.220
[Gift Record]

15:05.720 --> 15:07.300
Anyone who entered the Wei mansion without a gift

15:07.910 --> 15:09.530
must have ulterior motives.

15:10.360 --> 15:11.460
Using that condition

15:11.510 --> 15:12.610
to filter people out

15:13.240 --> 15:14.130
truly is a clever move.

15:17.840 --> 15:18.580
Miss Yu Wei,

15:19.030 --> 15:19.490
how come

15:19.790 --> 15:21.060
you didn't bring a gift either?

15:26.960 --> 15:28.940
I don't have the money.

15:32.240 --> 15:32.940
I'm sorry.

15:33.240 --> 15:34.220
It's fine.

15:37.240 --> 15:38.060
What now?

15:43.760 --> 15:45.580
The mark looks like a moon phase.

15:46.120 --> 15:47.700
And it's slowly shifting.

15:48.450 --> 15:49.820
Just now it was full.

15:50.840 --> 15:52.370
Now it's already a waning crescent.

15:57.000 --> 15:58.130
A death curse eats away

15:58.960 --> 16:00.010
at one's lifespan day by day.

16:01.870 --> 16:03.180
Once it's fully consumed, one will be dead.

16:04.870 --> 16:05.980
I don't want to die.

16:06.240 --> 16:07.480
We may have been cursed,

16:07.750 --> 16:08.850
but we've gained something too.

16:09.440 --> 16:10.890
The suspect pool just got a lot smaller,

16:11.910 --> 16:12.530
didn't it?

16:14.440 --> 16:15.730
I assume the three of you don't have

16:16.120 --> 16:17.100
the curse mark on your hands, right?

16:24.150 --> 16:24.820
Pig.

16:27.910 --> 16:28.340
You...

17:03.080 --> 17:04.490
Of the three people without the curse mark,

17:05.120 --> 17:06.180
Liu Weixue is the one I suspect most.

17:06.840 --> 17:07.650
He was so drunk he could barely

17:07.670 --> 17:08.570
tell east from west,

17:09.480 --> 17:10.430
yet somehow he happened

17:10.690 --> 17:11.860
to stagger into the weaving workshop?

17:12.720 --> 17:13.380
I don't buy it.

17:13.750 --> 17:14.700
Good. You shouldn't.

17:16.240 --> 17:17.900
He went there specifically to find Luo Wei.

17:19.850 --> 17:20.660
Luo Wei?

17:36.350 --> 17:37.330
What's that?

17:38.830 --> 17:40.770
Master Wu Shiguang set up a barrier.

17:42.960 --> 17:44.980
He said it could stop demons from hurting people.

17:48.110 --> 17:48.810
Good.

17:49.440 --> 17:50.050
Good.

17:51.200 --> 17:53.050
Have some tea and sober up.

17:54.160 --> 17:54.940
Young Master Liu,

17:55.590 --> 17:57.250
please don't drink so much again.

17:58.030 --> 17:58.940
It's too hard on your body.

18:01.110 --> 18:02.330
I only drank that much

18:02.750 --> 18:04.140
because I was shielding you from the wine.

18:05.070 --> 18:05.770
Luo Wei...

18:16.270 --> 18:17.730
What do I have to do

18:20.000 --> 18:21.810
for you to finally care about me?

18:23.510 --> 18:24.330
Young Master Liu,

18:25.750 --> 18:27.010
fate is predetermined.

18:28.750 --> 18:29.770
It can't be forced.

18:31.400 --> 18:33.250
Everyone says Weimiao Pavilion is the best place

18:33.270 --> 18:34.140
to pray for love.

18:34.920 --> 18:36.330
If I went to ask for a talisman,

18:37.240 --> 18:38.180
would your heart...

18:39.480 --> 18:40.660
would your heart

18:40.680 --> 18:41.530
finally be mine?

18:45.310 --> 18:46.700
But anyone can see

18:47.310 --> 18:48.700
Wei Qing is the only one Luo Wei loves.

18:50.590 --> 18:51.380
The Wei mansion

18:51.550 --> 18:52.380
may not be big,

18:52.880 --> 18:54.380
but the relationships here are all tangled up.

18:56.070 --> 18:57.330
What a headache.

18:58.640 --> 19:00.010
He was obviously drunk.

19:02.400 --> 19:03.420
How could he have killed anyone?

19:03.960 --> 19:05.050
Ms. Yu said

19:06.400 --> 19:07.490
that last night, Steward Luo took her

19:07.720 --> 19:09.530
to the weaving workshop right after she entered the Wei mansion.

19:10.200 --> 19:11.940
She and Steward Luo can vouch for each other.

19:26.350 --> 19:27.460
Vouching for each other

19:28.400 --> 19:29.980
can also mean covering for each other.

19:40.510 --> 19:41.180
What a headache.

19:42.400 --> 19:43.730
Why does everyone seem innocent

19:44.240 --> 19:45.220
and suspicious at the same time?

19:46.070 --> 19:46.700
It's driving me crazy.

19:47.240 --> 19:48.390
Who is Xiaowei, really?

19:49.400 --> 19:49.940
Don't worry.

19:50.400 --> 19:51.420
A fox

19:52.030 --> 19:53.570
will show its tail sooner or later.

19:55.640 --> 19:56.330
What's wrong?

20:02.320 --> 20:03.300
I've lost my sense of touch.

20:04.280 --> 20:05.130
What do we do now?

20:06.200 --> 20:07.530
I don't want to be the one to bury you.

20:07.800 --> 20:08.420
Shut up.

20:08.960 --> 20:09.880
If I were Xiaowei,

20:10.680 --> 20:11.810
I'd put the death curse

20:11.860 --> 20:12.730
on myself too.

20:13.920 --> 20:15.770
But when that scream rang out...

20:18.920 --> 20:19.620
Wu Wangyan,

20:19.750 --> 20:20.940
Ji Ling, Li Jie,

20:21.200 --> 20:22.620
and Yu Wei were all with you.

20:24.000 --> 20:25.250
Who would've had time to rip out a heart?

20:25.720 --> 20:26.660
There are countless demonic arts.

20:27.550 --> 20:29.330
A demon can kill from 1,000 li away.

20:30.310 --> 20:30.900
Besides,

20:31.200 --> 20:32.570
what if Xiaowei wasn't working alone?

20:33.110 --> 20:34.180
Couldn't she have had an accomplice?

20:35.640 --> 20:36.460
Good point.

20:36.830 --> 20:38.490
Even I've got a capable right-hand man

20:39.030 --> 20:40.010
like you.

20:41.880 --> 20:42.730
Who do you suspect most?

20:45.350 --> 20:46.050
Wu Wangyan.

20:49.240 --> 20:49.940
And Yu Wei.

20:56.400 --> 20:56.940
Wangyan,

20:58.480 --> 20:59.460
what are you doing?

21:01.590 --> 21:03.220
The death curse is starting to take effect.

21:04.110 --> 21:05.290
I've lost my sense of touch.

21:06.110 --> 21:06.940
It doesn't hurt.

21:10.200 --> 21:11.340
Don't worry.

21:12.440 --> 21:13.090
Right,

21:13.880 --> 21:14.870
and there's Ji Ling too.

21:15.070 --> 21:16.530
He's just an ordinary demon hunter

21:16.530 --> 21:17.600
with no sacred power,

21:18.240 --> 21:19.460
yet that Shilin Sect commander

21:19.590 --> 21:21.090
obeys him without question and never leaves his side.

21:21.920 --> 21:22.700
Something's definitely off.

21:26.400 --> 21:28.330
I can't even taste these roasted ginkgo nuts anymore.

21:28.920 --> 21:29.660
This is awful.

21:30.110 --> 21:31.490
The death curse will gradually strip away

21:31.550 --> 21:32.460
our senses

21:33.030 --> 21:34.650
until all five are gone.

21:35.160 --> 21:37.210
The day this mark turns completely dark

21:37.590 --> 21:39.490
will be the day we die.

21:40.750 --> 21:42.510
Xiaowei truly is vile.

21:43.480 --> 21:44.330
We've got to find a way

21:44.920 --> 21:46.250
to make her slip up and show herself.

21:48.640 --> 21:49.810
The Shilin Sect's demon hunters

21:49.830 --> 21:51.050
obey their commander.

21:51.510 --> 21:52.220
Who does the commander

21:53.200 --> 21:53.980
answer to?

21:54.350 --> 21:55.090
The Dragon Deity.

21:59.350 --> 22:00.530
The Dragon Deity?

22:02.070 --> 22:03.010
No way.

22:03.680 --> 22:04.620
That silly boy

22:05.070 --> 22:05.810
is the Dragon Deity?

22:06.240 --> 22:07.980
But how could the Dragon Deity have no sacred power?

22:08.960 --> 22:09.770
There's always been a rumor

22:10.070 --> 22:11.940
that Chi wen was badly wounded

22:12.030 --> 22:12.860
in that great calamity

22:13.240 --> 22:14.770
and lost all of his Dragon Deity's Power.

22:17.880 --> 22:18.990
Do you remember the ring

22:18.990 --> 22:19.900
on Ji Ling's hand?

22:21.400 --> 22:22.620
He was able to use demon magic

22:23.550 --> 22:25.420
only with the help of that ring.

22:26.000 --> 22:27.730
We tracked the demonic energy here.

22:28.080 --> 22:29.570
You're the heart-ripping nine-tailed fox!

22:31.200 --> 22:32.700
Then isn't this just what we wanted?

22:33.310 --> 22:34.900
Now we can kill the Dragon Deity

22:36.270 --> 22:37.290
without going to the Shilin Sect.

22:39.030 --> 22:40.460
I don't think it's that simple.

22:40.920 --> 22:42.010
Let's wait a bit longer.

22:44.270 --> 22:45.250
We need to survive first.

22:49.920 --> 22:51.050
Now, I need to make a trip.

22:53.490 --> 22:54.510
Weimiao Pavilion?

22:55.550 --> 22:56.290
Wangyan,

22:57.790 --> 22:59.010
what's your plan?

23:00.680 --> 23:02.140
Are we really just going to sit here

23:04.590 --> 23:05.570
and wait for the death curse

23:07.750 --> 23:09.280
to take our lives?

23:10.030 --> 23:11.280
Catch Xiaowei,

23:11.880 --> 23:13.670
and the death curse will be lifted.

23:14.590 --> 23:16.530
Besides, Ji Ling and Wu Shiguang

23:16.550 --> 23:17.700
are cursed too.

23:19.000 --> 23:20.620
They won't sit around waiting to die.

23:22.240 --> 23:23.090
They're even

23:24.000 --> 23:24.940
more anxious than we are.

23:27.410 --> 23:29.010
Are they really that powerful?

23:30.070 --> 23:31.220
Let's not even get into the rest.

23:32.030 --> 23:33.860
Wu Shiguang's prayer bead bracelet alone

23:33.880 --> 23:35.220
is no ordinary artifact.

23:35.510 --> 23:36.710
It's called the Twelve Thoughts.

23:37.310 --> 23:39.020
The beads were forged from the blood

23:39.020 --> 23:40.950
of 12 vicious sinners

23:41.110 --> 23:43.290
and embody 12 different kinds of thought:

23:44.000 --> 23:44.860
benevolence,

23:45.270 --> 23:45.940
malice,

23:46.830 --> 23:47.660
greed,

23:48.720 --> 23:49.570
obsession,

23:50.440 --> 23:51.250
desire,

23:51.920 --> 23:52.730
delusion...

23:53.310 --> 23:54.420
All right, enough.

23:56.030 --> 23:58.140
If that artifact is really so powerful,

23:59.310 --> 24:00.520
how did it end up in the hands

24:00.520 --> 24:02.230
of some wandering demon hunter?

24:04.110 --> 24:05.620
Do you really think he's just

24:05.620 --> 24:07.510
some ordinary wandering demon hunter?

24:10.440 --> 24:11.380
What about Ji Ling?

24:15.030 --> 24:15.810
What do you think?

24:21.680 --> 24:23.570
He's clearly a simple-minded fool.

24:24.240 --> 24:25.530
Smile at him,

24:26.200 --> 24:27.250
and he'd hand over his life to you.

24:31.240 --> 24:32.140
Wrong.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.380
He's even more mysterious

24:34.640 --> 24:35.730
than Wu Shiguang.

24:36.510 --> 24:37.620
Don't let your guard down.

24:39.790 --> 24:40.700
Interesting.

24:43.440 --> 24:44.620
Then I'll go spend some time

24:44.640 --> 24:46.050
with this man fate chose for me.

25:00.550 --> 25:01.380
You scared me.

25:02.200 --> 25:03.010
I found nothing.

25:53.550 --> 25:54.330
Actually, I...

26:02.550 --> 26:03.420
Miss Yu Wei,

26:04.400 --> 26:05.900
you hit me way too hard.

26:07.110 --> 26:09.420
Why did you hide in there? You scared me.

26:10.110 --> 26:11.570
I thought

26:12.100 --> 26:13.980
you were some creep.

26:14.030 --> 26:15.620
You clearly saw it was me.

26:17.030 --> 26:18.220
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

26:19.440 --> 26:20.420
It was

26:21.270 --> 26:22.810
so dark in there.

26:23.680 --> 26:25.220
I couldn't see clearly at all.

26:27.920 --> 26:28.290
Well,

26:29.830 --> 26:31.220
can you see clearly now?

26:33.350 --> 26:34.620
I should have the kind of face

26:35.720 --> 26:37.530
people never forget, right?

26:39.200 --> 26:39.770
Very handsome.

26:41.110 --> 26:43.380
So tell me,

26:45.070 --> 26:46.050
do you think

26:46.830 --> 26:47.730
I'm handsome?

26:49.680 --> 26:51.530
Or do I look familiar to you?

26:53.010 --> 26:53.900
Not at all.

26:54.920 --> 26:55.730
I don't look familiar?

26:56.310 --> 26:57.220
She means not handsome.

27:00.030 --> 27:00.660
Thanks.

27:05.350 --> 27:07.220
Why are you in Luo Wei's room?

27:08.550 --> 27:10.000
And why were you hiding in the cabinet?

27:10.960 --> 27:11.980
We're here to investigate.

27:12.160 --> 27:12.620
What about you?

27:13.160 --> 27:14.380
I'm here to investigate too.

27:16.480 --> 27:17.050
You...

27:17.510 --> 27:18.530
you're here to hunt the demon too?

27:19.070 --> 27:20.180
Are you a demon hunter?

27:20.720 --> 27:21.940
Are you a demon hunter?

27:24.750 --> 27:26.370
I'm just an ordinary person.

27:26.640 --> 27:28.180
How could I be a demon hunter?

27:28.440 --> 27:29.730
I'm only investigating

27:29.790 --> 27:31.130
to save my own life.

27:31.240 --> 27:32.900
If we don't find Xiaowei soon,

27:35.750 --> 27:36.770
how are we supposed

27:37.680 --> 27:38.770
to break this death curse?

27:42.760 --> 27:44.010
I found Steward Luo

27:44.010 --> 27:45.050
very suspicious,

27:45.830 --> 27:47.180
so I thought I'd start with her.

27:52.590 --> 27:53.180
Everyone,

27:53.200 --> 27:54.090
we're here.

27:54.750 --> 27:55.660
Watch your step.

27:57.100 --> 27:57.620
We're here.

27:57.640 --> 27:58.820
Watch your step.

27:58.830 --> 27:59.490
This is the place.

28:12.880 --> 28:13.530
This way.

28:17.350 --> 28:18.900
Let's hang ours over here.

28:35.310 --> 28:36.220
The Energy-Draining Spell?

28:39.500 --> 28:41.540
[Weimiao Pavilion]

28:44.640 --> 28:46.140
Looks like someone's hiding inside,

28:47.790 --> 28:49.460
cultivating demon magic by absorbing

28:51.000 --> 28:52.050
mortals' heart energy.

28:54.510 --> 28:55.330
Someone?

28:55.660 --> 28:56.700
You mean a demon.

28:57.000 --> 28:57.810
Be careful.

29:00.270 --> 29:01.290
Yes, Lady Wei.

29:01.750 --> 29:02.460
Understood.

29:02.750 --> 29:03.420
I'll handle it now.

29:12.310 --> 29:12.940
Miss,

29:14.070 --> 29:15.330
what do people pray for

29:15.330 --> 29:16.220
at Weimiao Pavilion?

29:16.790 --> 29:18.220
This is a pavilion of love.

29:18.680 --> 29:20.220
People come here to pray for romance, of course.

29:22.310 --> 29:24.380
So that's where all that heart energy comes from.

29:25.000 --> 29:26.460
No wonder I see pink everywhere.

29:27.270 --> 29:28.420
He's so handsome.

29:28.830 --> 29:30.570
It can't be happening this fast, can it?

29:30.880 --> 29:32.860
This place really works.

29:33.080 --> 29:33.790
Darling,

29:33.790 --> 29:35.690
why did you walk so fast?

29:35.880 --> 29:37.220
You should've waited for me.

29:43.160 --> 29:43.770
Miss,

29:44.440 --> 29:45.840
I've heard that praying for love

29:45.920 --> 29:47.120
at Weimiao Pavilion really works.

29:47.550 --> 29:48.140
Is that true?

29:49.640 --> 29:51.050
I used to think so too.

29:51.880 --> 29:53.180
Now?

29:53.830 --> 29:54.490
I'd say it's just so-so.

29:55.680 --> 29:57.210
But they all say the love talismans here

29:57.210 --> 29:58.220
work wonders.

29:59.160 --> 30:00.770
You two don't really look

30:01.240 --> 30:02.090
like you need

30:02.110 --> 30:03.850
Lady Wei's love talisman.

30:04.680 --> 30:05.320
We...

30:05.320 --> 30:06.290
Lady Wei?

30:07.350 --> 30:08.210
Anyway,

30:08.400 --> 30:09.810
if you really want one...

30:37.780 --> 30:38.730
What did she tell you?

30:39.700 --> 30:40.570
Curious?

30:42.200 --> 30:42.780
I am.

30:43.110 --> 30:44.060
Beg, and I'll tell.

30:51.310 --> 30:52.370
She said

30:53.000 --> 30:54.760
that if you wanted a love talisman,

30:55.200 --> 30:56.850
you'd have to take off all your clothes

30:57.110 --> 30:58.880
and bare yourself completely.

31:00.270 --> 31:01.460
I wasn't finished.

31:02.400 --> 31:03.870
After you take off your clothes,

31:03.920 --> 31:05.900
you need to tell Lady Wei a secret.

31:06.400 --> 31:07.460
You're making this up.

31:07.590 --> 31:09.240
Remember? I don't lie.

31:10.270 --> 31:12.180
You have to undress to go inside and ask for a talisman?

31:14.830 --> 31:15.380
Also,

31:16.030 --> 31:16.900
why are you following me?

31:22.880 --> 31:25.200
Tanghulu!

31:26.040 --> 31:28.320
Tanghulu!

31:28.440 --> 31:31.110
Scented sachets and pendants!

31:36.400 --> 31:37.380
I wasn't

31:37.590 --> 31:38.810
following you.

31:43.000 --> 31:43.860
You're suspicious of her?

31:46.880 --> 31:48.700
But last night, she was with Ms. Yu all night.

31:52.160 --> 31:53.530
I wasn't exactly with her all night.

31:54.830 --> 31:56.010
There are too many guests.

31:56.310 --> 31:57.420
We can't let them find out

31:57.510 --> 31:58.810
the bride never went through with the ceremony.

31:59.310 --> 32:00.220
I'll take you

32:00.400 --> 32:01.460
to the weaving workshop. Hide there for now.

32:06.590 --> 32:08.850
After Steward Luo took me to the weaving workshop,

32:08.960 --> 32:09.730
she left.

32:10.790 --> 32:11.570
I asked her

32:11.830 --> 32:13.330
to bring Wei Qing to me.

32:15.640 --> 32:17.330
I was worried about Master Wei's safety,

32:17.880 --> 32:18.980
so I secretly asked

32:19.030 --> 32:21.010
Master Wu Shiguang to pose as the groom.

32:21.680 --> 32:23.090
But she knew

32:23.920 --> 32:24.980
Wei Qing was locked

32:25.000 --> 32:26.220
inside a cabinet in the workshop.

32:27.160 --> 32:27.940
Exactly.

32:28.440 --> 32:29.770
Such a blatant contradiction.

32:30.550 --> 32:31.380
Now,

32:32.000 --> 32:33.180
don't you think

32:33.350 --> 32:34.220
she's highly suspicious?

32:34.960 --> 32:36.330
Luo Wei's only been at the Wei mansion

32:36.330 --> 32:37.530
for a little over a month.

32:38.030 --> 32:39.400
No one in the household

32:39.480 --> 32:40.870
knows where she came from.

32:41.270 --> 32:42.460
She's the only outsider living here.

32:43.000 --> 32:43.660
Don't you think

32:44.070 --> 32:45.180
she's highly suspicious?

32:46.550 --> 32:47.380
We've already

32:47.590 --> 32:48.660
looked into Luo Wei.

32:55.000 --> 32:55.700
Luo Wei,

32:56.240 --> 32:57.620
born in the old town,

32:58.310 --> 32:59.220
is an orphan

33:00.160 --> 33:01.980
and was raised by a rural healer.

33:02.870 --> 33:04.040
It is said that the healer

33:04.230 --> 33:05.510
knew a thing or two about poison.

33:06.480 --> 33:07.740
We suspected

33:07.920 --> 33:09.300
she poisoned Wei Qing,

33:09.400 --> 33:10.500
so we came to her room to look for evidence.

33:12.000 --> 33:13.610
I knew something was off about her.

33:15.400 --> 33:17.180
Thank goodness we have you, Mr. Ji.

33:17.990 --> 33:18.700
Otherwise,

33:20.040 --> 33:21.130
the whole Wei family

33:21.150 --> 33:22.130
would've been destroyed.

33:23.720 --> 33:24.650
You're not a demon hunter,

33:25.270 --> 33:26.090
so don't worry about it.

33:27.040 --> 33:28.220
That fox demon is dangerous.

33:28.600 --> 33:30.340
Leave it to the Shilin Sect to deal with her.

33:32.550 --> 33:34.500
That other Shilin Sect hunter

33:34.500 --> 33:35.450
was too weak.

33:36.890 --> 33:37.810
Mr. Ji,

33:38.000 --> 33:39.540
if you'd come a little sooner,

33:39.640 --> 33:41.090
I would've had someone to rely on.

33:44.110 --> 33:44.810
Ji,

33:46.000 --> 33:46.770
thank you.

33:52.350 --> 33:54.290
"Ji"?

33:56.640 --> 33:57.850
I'm just worried about my cousin.

34:00.550 --> 34:01.890
You mean Ms. Yu Shengwei?

34:03.230 --> 34:04.370
You two are so close.

34:05.680 --> 34:06.620
At a time like this,

34:07.240 --> 34:08.250
how can Luo Wei still be in the mood

34:08.270 --> 34:08.980
to pray for love?

34:10.240 --> 34:11.810
Is she really in love with Wei Qing?

34:13.070 --> 34:14.260
Shiguang,

34:14.480 --> 34:15.730
I'm afraid you've never seen

34:15.730 --> 34:17.740
what a woman who's truly in love

34:17.800 --> 34:19.090
looks like.

34:19.280 --> 34:20.050
My surname is Wu.

34:20.880 --> 34:21.940
You can call me Master Wu.

34:22.840 --> 34:23.860
Love

34:24.070 --> 34:25.760
can make someone holding a sharp blade

34:25.760 --> 34:27.090
cast aside their weapon.

34:27.230 --> 34:29.300
It can make the proud and arrogant lower their heads.

34:29.710 --> 34:31.650
It can make someone clad in armor show their weakness.

34:32.670 --> 34:34.220
It can make the cleverest person

34:34.310 --> 34:37.070
do the stupidest things in the world.

34:37.400 --> 34:39.170
It can even make one forget where they came from

34:39.480 --> 34:40.420
and where they're going.

34:43.440 --> 34:44.260
I came by boat,

34:45.030 --> 34:46.420
and I plan to walk back later.

34:47.960 --> 34:48.570
Look.

34:49.110 --> 34:49.940
What is this?

34:51.400 --> 34:52.090
Wood.

34:54.110 --> 34:55.490
That's what you're made of.

34:58.150 --> 34:59.460
You make mutual love

35:00.190 --> 35:01.300
between a man and a woman

35:01.920 --> 35:03.460
sound like some kind of sorcery.

35:03.880 --> 35:05.260
Love

35:05.360 --> 35:06.470
is sorcery.

35:07.280 --> 35:07.820
No,

35:08.230 --> 35:09.790
it's even more terrifying than sorcery.

35:10.360 --> 35:11.090
Tell me,

35:11.510 --> 35:12.460
does Luo Wei strike you

35:12.550 --> 35:13.690
as someone who would

35:13.710 --> 35:15.050
do crazy things for love?

35:18.550 --> 35:20.230
Compared with ordinary women,

35:20.400 --> 35:21.460
she's far more meticulous,

35:22.190 --> 35:23.090
and she hides her sharpness deep within.

35:23.920 --> 35:24.690
So, no, she doesn't.

35:24.880 --> 35:26.380
Shiguang, you're so clever.

35:27.000 --> 35:28.340
Wangyan, your name suits you well.

35:28.710 --> 35:29.340
Thanks.

35:46.670 --> 35:47.300
Found it.

35:50.360 --> 35:51.090
Mr. Ji,

35:52.320 --> 35:53.530
if you don't let go of my hand,

35:54.480 --> 35:55.530
how am I supposed to give it to you?

36:08.110 --> 36:08.650
Here.

36:16.070 --> 36:16.780
It's the antidote.

36:18.590 --> 36:19.980
You can tell just by smelling it?

36:20.320 --> 36:20.980
I am

36:21.230 --> 36:22.690
a pharmacology genius who's read widely.

36:23.550 --> 36:24.420
The evidence is conclusive now.

36:26.030 --> 36:27.420
Looks like beautiful women

36:27.920 --> 36:28.780
are all liars.

36:31.800 --> 36:33.650
Why are you insulting yourself?

36:37.110 --> 36:38.420
So you think I'm pretty, Ji?

36:41.880 --> 36:42.650
I think

36:42.960 --> 36:44.170
we've all underestimated Luo Wei.

36:44.840 --> 36:46.490
Jealousy born of unrequited love

36:46.670 --> 36:48.340
is only her disguise.

36:49.190 --> 36:50.260
What she really wants

36:50.920 --> 36:51.690
isn't Wei Qing.

36:52.840 --> 36:53.900
It's this entire Wei mansion.

36:58.440 --> 36:59.170
Miss Yu Wei.

37:09.800 --> 37:10.790
Come on, let's go.

37:10.880 --> 37:11.850
Why are you still standing there?

37:12.590 --> 37:13.740
"Zhao Xiao'e."

37:14.110 --> 37:14.820
What?

37:19.920 --> 37:21.300
The wife

37:22.070 --> 37:23.050
of one of the victims

37:23.110 --> 37:24.380
is named Zhao Xiao'e.

37:25.220 --> 37:27.920
[Zhao Xiao'e]

37:27.920 --> 37:29.460
Wake up!

37:38.230 --> 37:39.650
Li Mao, the man who died at the Wei mansion last night,

37:41.030 --> 37:42.300
was holding this talisman too.

37:44.400 --> 37:45.610
I also came here

37:46.550 --> 37:47.300
because of this talisman.

37:48.800 --> 37:49.650
Could it be

37:50.670 --> 37:51.940
that all the victims' partners

37:52.670 --> 37:54.050
once came to Weimiao Pavilion?

37:58.590 --> 37:59.650
We'll know once we look.

38:03.360 --> 38:04.260
"Chen Geng"?

38:18.150 --> 38:18.980
"Sun Zhiniang."

38:33.400 --> 38:34.300
[Tao Xi]
Li Mao's wife,

38:34.920 --> 38:35.610
Tao Xi.

38:48.440 --> 38:49.130
It seems

38:50.510 --> 38:51.570
we really do need to go inside.

38:53.340 --> 38:57.060
[Weimiao Pavilion]

39:19.230 --> 39:19.740
He's awake.

39:25.590 --> 39:26.260
Easy now.

39:26.550 --> 39:27.420
What happened to me?

39:28.070 --> 39:28.820
You were poisoned,

39:29.230 --> 39:30.650
but you're fine now.

39:31.840 --> 39:32.690
Poisoned?

39:35.030 --> 39:36.170
Why don't I remember anything?

39:36.670 --> 39:38.340
Luo Wei poisoned you.

39:39.630 --> 39:40.420
Luo Wei?

39:43.760 --> 39:45.090
Why would she do that?

39:47.710 --> 39:48.300
Where is she?

39:48.350 --> 39:49.190
I need to find her.

39:50.710 --> 39:52.300
You... you should rest first.

40:12.590 --> 40:13.540
A couple coming here together

40:13.540 --> 40:14.860
to pray for love? That's new.

40:15.280 --> 40:15.980
How interesting.

40:17.440 --> 40:18.650
- We're not... - What can we do?

40:19.030 --> 40:20.340
We just love each other too much.

40:20.710 --> 40:22.090
We're here to pray

40:22.190 --> 40:23.490
that we'll still be a couple in the next life.

40:24.120 --> 40:25.050
Isn't that right, darling?

40:25.510 --> 40:26.970
Lady Wei is out traveling.

40:27.180 --> 40:28.330
She won't be here for quite a while.

40:28.760 --> 40:30.170
Please come back another time.

40:30.470 --> 40:32.090
But someone just came out with a talisman.

40:37.240 --> 40:38.980
Lady Wei isn't here,

40:39.510 --> 40:40.820
but if you follow the rules,

40:41.320 --> 40:42.940
the love talisman may still be granted.

40:45.840 --> 40:46.490
I don't have any money.

40:54.480 --> 40:55.190
Really, I don't.

41:07.550 --> 41:08.740
Besides a donation,

41:08.800 --> 41:09.940
you also have to write down a secret

41:10.230 --> 41:11.340
and put it in the box.

41:13.590 --> 41:14.090
A secret?

41:15.400 --> 41:16.090
Why?

41:16.630 --> 41:17.980
Lady Wei likes secrets.

41:18.440 --> 41:19.890
She thinks they are

41:19.890 --> 41:20.810
the most powerful force in the world.

41:21.150 --> 41:22.090
Besides,

41:22.150 --> 41:23.740
isn't mortals' unrequited love

41:23.800 --> 41:24.780
a kind of secret too?

41:28.030 --> 41:28.740
Fair point.

42:02.080 --> 42:02.960
My...

42:03.470 --> 42:04.090
copper coin.

42:04.200 --> 42:05.770
Looks like what you wrote was a lie.

42:06.440 --> 42:07.530
Without sincerity,

42:07.800 --> 42:09.460
you'll never get a talisman that works.

42:09.760 --> 42:10.420
Leave now.

42:10.880 --> 42:11.740
Stop wasting your time.

42:14.320 --> 42:15.300
I told you so.

42:16.110 --> 42:17.130
We shouldn't have bothered.

42:43.480 --> 42:44.840
Hiding private savings, are you?

42:47.710 --> 42:48.880
If you don't want to die,

42:50.000 --> 42:52.170
answer my questions.

42:53.670 --> 42:54.940
Are the heart-ripping murders in the city

42:55.840 --> 42:57.530
connected to the love talismans

42:57.840 --> 42:59.010
you handed out?

43:00.110 --> 43:01.260
This concerns Lady Wei.

43:02.070 --> 43:03.210
Even if you kill me,

43:03.590 --> 43:04.570
I won't say a word.

43:10.550 --> 43:11.260
Let me.

43:14.840 --> 43:15.530
Tell me.

43:16.510 --> 43:17.690
Are the heart-ripping murders in the city

43:18.070 --> 43:19.610
connected to the love talismans

43:20.400 --> 43:21.690
you handed out?

43:22.880 --> 43:25.340
The love talismans carry a Fox-Allure Spell.

43:25.960 --> 43:27.530
They can make the one who asks for the talisman

43:27.920 --> 43:29.650
win the affection of the one they love

43:30.110 --> 43:31.690
and become their partner.

43:32.920 --> 43:34.110
Is there a price to pay?

43:35.070 --> 43:37.540
If the one who asked for the talisman falls for someone else

43:37.840 --> 43:38.900
and regrets the union,

43:39.510 --> 43:41.170
they can tear up the talisman,

43:41.670 --> 43:42.860
but their partner

43:43.070 --> 43:44.400
will suffer the consequences.

43:44.710 --> 43:46.050
They'll be racked with heartache.

43:46.590 --> 43:47.340
Eventually,

43:47.800 --> 43:49.530
they'll rip out their own heart and die.

43:58.030 --> 43:59.590
When the one who asked for the talisman falls for someone else,

44:00.190 --> 44:01.740
their partner will die.

44:03.230 --> 44:05.180
What a vicious spell.

44:19.260 --> 44:20.420
♪It's your light♪

44:20.620 --> 44:22.500
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

44:22.660 --> 44:25.780
♪That set the night alight♪

44:26.140 --> 44:32.660
♪And lead me through the fight♪

44:34.420 --> 44:36.300
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

44:36.740 --> 44:41.180
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

44:41.980 --> 44:43.660
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

44:43.820 --> 44:49.220
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

44:49.980 --> 44:55.380
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

44:57.700 --> 45:03.740
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

45:04.700 --> 45:06.860
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

45:07.140 --> 45:11.980
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

45:12.340 --> 45:14.660
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

45:14.860 --> 45:19.940
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

45:20.180 --> 45:22.180
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

45:22.460 --> 45:26.820
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

45:27.820 --> 45:34.780
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

45:51.340 --> 45:54.300
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

45:55.380 --> 45:58.780
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

45:59.580 --> 46:02.100
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

46:02.340 --> 46:05.420
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

46:05.820 --> 46:08.140
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

46:08.660 --> 46:13.060
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

46:13.300 --> 46:15.460
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

46:15.860 --> 46:20.820
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

46:21.060 --> 46:22.220
♪It's your light♪

46:22.420 --> 46:24.260
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

46:24.460 --> 46:27.580
♪That set the night alight♪

46:28.340 --> 46:37.780
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
